@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_aktllq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.77 + v2 + 0.21) * wp.cos(v0 + 0.23)) + 0.54)
    v2 = (0.85 - wp.exp((v1 + 0.94 + tmp + 0.37)))
    v0 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.05 - tmp + 0.65)) / ((tmp + 0.63 - v2 + 0.22) + 0.69))
    data[tid] = v0
